
Implement Student ID Card generation and printable view.

Reference:
- StudentController
- Student DataTable listing (Grades/Students style)
- Existing action buttons pattern (view/edit/delete)

Requirements:

=================================================
1. Add ID Card Action Button
=================================================

In Student listing DataTable actions column, add new button:

- ID Card (Print icon)

Example:
- Eye (View)
- Edit
- Delete
- ID Card (NEW)

Button behavior:
- Opens ID card page OR printable modal
- Uses student_id

Route example:
GET /students/{id}/id-card

=================================================
2. ID Card Page (Printable)
=================================================

Create dedicated Blade view:

students/id_card.blade.php

Page must be print-friendly.

Add:
- Print button (top right)
- Auto print CSS support (optional)

=================================================
3. ID Card Layout
=================================================

Design a single student ID card layout containing:

TOP SECTION:
- Profile Picture (student photo)

MAIN DETAILS:

- Student Name
- Class
- Faculty (if available)
- Roll No
- Date of Birth
- Blood Group

PARENT INFO:
- Father’s Name
- Address

=================================================
4. Signature Section (Bottom)
=================================================

Add two signature placeholders:

------------------------
Principal Signature
------------------------

------------------------
Guardian Signature
------------------------

=================================================
5. Data Source
=================================================

Load student data including:

- students table
- student_fiscal_details (current active fiscal year)
- class
- faculty
- parent relationship

Ensure active fiscal year record is used.

=================================================
6. Print Styling
=================================================

Add CSS:

- A6 or ID card size layout
- Center aligned card
- Border styled card
- Hidden navigation when printing
- Clean typography

@media print {
  .no-print { display: none; }
}

=================================================
7. Controller Method
=================================================

Add method:

StudentController@idCard($id)

Responsibilities:
- Load student with relationships
- Fetch active fiscal year detail
- Return view

=================================================
8. Optional (Advanced)
=================================================

If project uses DataTables heavily:

- Allow "Print ID Card" from modal OR new tab
- Ensure route is fast and lightweight

=================================================
9. Output
=================================================

Generate:
- Route
- Controller method
- Blade view
- DataTable action button update
- Print CSS

Follow existing UI style and keep implementation minimal and consistent with current system.